{"tid":1822294,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【抵制TVB】一人一電郵要求麗星郵輪（雲頂集團）停止用TVB偽人開Show","createTime":"2020-01-13T01:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T16:43:10.000Z","uid":113630,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"7cacacb0823a6fcd1d40773844b3be91b6837f59","tid":1822294,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:04:46.000Z","msg":"【抵制TVB任務⚔️為麗星郵輪🚢炮製：電郵攻勢】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dY2mjA9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdY2mjA9.jpg&h=b82c317c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雲頂集團係馬來西亞最大嘅娛樂賭業集團，業務有雲頂高原、麗星郵輪同星夢郵輪等等。無論喺香港定係大馬，佢哋一樣經常搵CCTVB偽人開Show。其實TVB本身都係一艘沉緊嘅船啦🤷🏻&zwj;♀️！上郵輪🚢睇Show，因住變鐵達尼呀！<br />\n<br />\n麗星郵輪<br />\n27/02/2016 蕭正楠海上演唱會<br />\n21/05/2019 鄭俊弘音樂會<br />\n31/12/2019 張景淳音樂會<br />\n07/01/2020 陳山聰演唱會<br />\n13/02/2020 張國強、朱慧敏演唱會<br />\n<br />\n星夢郵輪<br />\n16/09/2017 吳岱融、歐瑞偉音樂會<br />\n14/10/2017 王浩信演唱會<br />\n09/11/2018 陳山聰、梁烈唯、黃子恆海上音樂會<br />\n14/06/2019 黎耀祥演唱會<br />\n17/08/2019 好兄弟－海上狂歡派對 （王梓軒、林盛斌、陳國峰、范振鋒與梁競徽）<br />\n12/10/2019 汪明荃&amp;羅家英演唱會<br />\n07/12/2019 葉麗儀、肥媽、陳潔靈演唱會<br />\n<br />\n大馬雲頂高原：<br />\n30/04/2016 陳展鵬胡定欣楊怡吳卓羲雲頂演唱會<br />\n01/12/2018 關菊英&amp;陳展鵬雲頂演唱會<br />\n18/05/2019 跳躍生命在雲頂 （馬德鐘、何廣沛、羅天宇、張彥博及張曦雯）<br />\n01/06/2019 媽妹祥祥爆滿雲頂演唱會 （肥媽、黑妹李麗霞、黎耀祥及阮兆祥）<br />\n10/08/2019 葉麗儀、肥媽、陳潔靈演唱會<br />\n10/11/2019 黃智雯演唱會<br />\n09/02/2020 梁競徽演唱會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢次嘅電郵攻勢就向雲頂集團請願，要佢哋停止搵TVB偽人唱歌，截斷呢個重要嘅偽人收入喇！😆</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>🔮電郵攻勢，簡單講係炸35個電郵，遊說各品牌唔好續廣告合約，流程簡略以下：<br />\n1️⃣ 開一個新電郵帳戶，或使用分身電郵<br />\n2️⃣ 將35個電郵清單copy and paste落收件人「密件副本 (bcc)」<br />\n3️⃣ Copy and paste電郵template，⚠️一定要改email title，改下款改日期<br />\n4️⃣ 完成！👍🏻🥰</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>💢如果電郵打回頭，解決方法：<br />\n1. 轉用Yahoo / Hotmail<br />\n2. 電郵title隔空格，請自行創作： P l e a s e   s t o p   i n v i t i n g   T V B   a r t i s t s</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n😎電郵清單入面有小編電郵，你哋有冇偷懶我哋完全掌握<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">🔶電郵及電郵template，請到Google doc (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2R8iU8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2R8iU8D&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=7a2dcfd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2R8iU8D</a>) ：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【35個電郵清單】<br />\ndigitalmarketing@starcruises.com, customerfeedback@rwgenting.com, customercare@rwgenting.com, pdp@rwgenting.com, ir.genm@genting.com, gbinfo@genting.com, career@genting.com, mccenq@resortsworldatsea.com, en.memberservices@dreamcruiseline.com, reservations.en@gentingcruiselines.com, cynthia.lee@starcruises.com, <a href=\"http://reservations.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Freservations.cn&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=220ccfb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">reservations.cn</a>@gentingcruiselines.com, hk.sales@starcruises.com, hk.marketing@starcruises.com, legal.privacy@gentinghk.com, mccenq@resortsworldatsea.com, cn.memberservices@dreamcruiseline.com, compliance@genting-securities.com, ccp.yuen.chi.wai@protonmail.com, customerservice@gentingcruiselines.com, sg.sales@starcruises.com, corporatesales@starcruises.com, sg.marketing@starcruises.com, mianne.pang@starcruises.com, reservations@dreamcruiseline.com, edwin.chui@starcruises.com, jennifer.leung@gentinghk.com, christine.li@gentinghk.com, yokesim.cheah@gentinghk.com, edith.poon@starcruises.com, corpcomm@gentinghk.com, hk.marketing.dc@dreamcruiseline.com, sg.sales@dreamcruiseline.com, kl.sales@dreamcruiseline.com, thatcher.brown@dreamcruiseline.com"},{"pid":"67da9d0a6ad4545407753e799661d11c241d5a58","tid":1822294,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:06:38.000Z","msg":"【電郵Template】<br />\n避免電郵被打回頭，每個字之間都有空格<br />\n有啲亂請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e0a6ab49986463adb06c2c41de6f0f44caa308","tid":1822294,"uid":113630,